captions.caption: Hey, I just met you, and this is crazy! But here's my number, so call me maybe?
I will eat just one, I swear!
Beauty is power; a smile is its sword.
They said I could become anything!
You're a beautiful, naive, sophisticated, newborn baby.
You're a cunning, pliable, chestnut-haired sunfish.
You're a poetic, noble land mermaid.
You're a beautiful, talented, brilliant, powerful musk ox.
Friendship is like peeing on yourself: everyone can see see it, but only you get the warm feeling that it brings.
It's true hard work never killed anybody, but why take the chance?
